Note that you can get an incredible speedup by wrapping the call to refresh() as follows:

viewer.getTable().setRedraw(false);
try {
  viewer.refresh();
} finally {
  viewer.getTable().setRedraw(true);
}

The numbers on my machine go down to about 100 ms if you do that.

